WEBVTT

00:04:27.980 --> 00:04:31.450
Alexa, who was 
the first president of India?

00:04:31.950 --> 00:04:35.790
Alexa: The first president of India 
was Rajendra Prasad.

00:04:35.880 --> 00:04:37.760
AR: No computer is needed,

00:04:37.760 --> 00:04:39.560
no need to open websites,

00:04:39.560 --> 00:04:43.520
you ask a question and in your simple 
language you have the answer.

00:04:43.760 --> 00:04:46.600
AI is making all this possible.

00:04:46.600 --> 00:04:50.440
AI understands what you want 
and then works on it sensibly.

00:04:50.440 --> 00:04:53.650
So this is from me to you, 
a new way of thinking.

00:04:54.080 --> 00:05:00.710
In times to come -- an AI world. 
AI that is intelligent, wise